 Shift</div></div></div>\",\"opts\":[],\"imgs\":[],\"href\":\"/past-years/jee/question/pa-given-object-takes-mathrmn-times-the-time-to-sli-jee-main-physics-motion-l6kn4hx1nb5yai1c\"},{\"i\":50,\"year\":2024,\"shift\":\"Morning Shift\",\"text\":\"A player caught a cricket ball of mass $$150 \\\\mathrm{~g}$$ moving at a speed of $$20 \\\\mathrm{~m} / \\\\mathrm{s}$$. If the catching process is completed in $$0.1 \\\\mathrm{~s}$$, the magnitude of force exerted by the ball on the hand of the player is:\",\"html\":\"<div class=\\\"bg-blue-500 text-white self-start w-[25px] h-[25px] shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center rounded-[50%] text-[80%]\\\">23</div> <div class=\\\"flex flex-col gap-2 lg:gap-4\\\"><div class=\\\"opacity-80 overflow-hidden min-w-0\\\" style=\\\"max-height: 140px\\\"><p>A player caught a cricket ball of mass $$150 \\\\mathrm{~g}$$ moving at a speed of $$20 \\\\mathrm{~m} / \\\\mathrm{s}$$. If the catching process is completed in $$0.1 \\\\mathrm{~s}$$, the magnitude of force exerted by the ball on the hand of the player is:</p></div> <div class=\\\"flex gap-2\\\"><div class=\\\"text-sm bg-green-500 text-green-500 bg-opacity-10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\\\">JEE Main 2024 (Online) 8th April Morning Shift</div></div></div>\",\"opts\":[],\"imgs\":[],\"href\":\"/past-years/jee/question/pa-player-caught-a-cricket-ball-of-mass-150-mathrmg-jee-main-physics-motion-xdsxbqzvqdom0b45\"},{\"i\":51,\"year\":2024,\"shift\":\"Evening Shift\",\"text\":\"A body of weight $$200 \\\\mathrm{~N}$$ is suspended from a tree branch through a chain of mass $$10 \\\\mathrm{~kg}$$. The branch pulls the chain by a force equal to (if $$\\\\mathrm{g}=10 \\\\mathrm{~m} / \\\\mathrm{s}^2$$) :\",\"html\":\"<div class=\\\"bg-blue-500 text-white self-start w-[25px] h-[25px] shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center rounded-[50%] text-[80%]\\\">24</div> <div class=\\\"flex flex-col gap-2 lg:gap-4\\\"><div class=\\\"opacity-80 overflow-hidden min-w-0\\\" style=\\\"max-height: 140px\\\"><p